tafsir[36]{c,v,t}:
  83,1,"Halkaare e perte ngoodanii ustoo…ìe peese."
  83,2,"…ìeen peesantee…ìe ummaade wo…ì…ìe …ìe …óa…ì…ìa timminaneede hakke mum en timmu…óo ko aldah e ustaare."
  83,3,"Si…ìe …ìetanii aade en wolla …ìe peesani …ìe, …ìe usta, ko nih yim…ìe Madiina ngonruno saanga fergo Nelaa…óo-yo o his- faade e mum en."
  83,4,"E …ìe golloobe …óe pankare pellitaani wonde ma…ìe ummitine faade e Alla?."
  83,5,"Na woodani haasboore e njobdi √±alngu teddungu ngam ko woni ko heen e musibbaaji e kul huli."
  83,6,"√±ande yimbe ummanii jom tago fof ngam haasbeede."
  83,7,"Huunde nde wonah no mbaadanir…óon nih wa*i wonde ummital alah caggal maayde, ko woni ko deftere faajiree…ìe nani ka to …ìuri lees…óude ka leydi."
  83,8,"Hol ko anndin Ma-aan nelaa…óo-hol ko woni sijjiin?."
  83,9,"Pellet deftere mum en ko winndaande, nde uytetaake nde …ìeydetaake."
  83,10,"Halkaare e perte woodanii e oon …óo √±alngu fennu…ìe …ìen."
  83,11,"…ìeen fennoo…ìe √±alaande njobdi nde, nde Alla yo…ìata heen jiyaa…ìe makko golle mum en ka aduna."
  83,12,"Fennatah oon …óo √±alngu si wonah palgu…óo keerol, keewdo bakkaat."
  83,13,"Si aayeeje amen tellinaa…óe e nelaa…óo Amen janngaama e mum, o wi*a: Ko tinndi le∆¥∆¥i gadiidi, wonah ko ummii ka Alla."
  83,14,"Huunde nde wonah no fennoo…ìe mbaadaniri nih, kono muuri …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe ko…ìe paggatii ko e goopi, …ìe nji*iraani goongo …ìer…óe mum en."
  83,15,"Ko goongo kam…ìe de ko…ìe ha…óaa…ìe yiide joomi mum en √±ande darnga."
  83,16,"Refti kam…ìe ko…ìe naatoo…ìe yiite, …ìe tampa e nguli henge."
  83,17,"Refti …ìe wi*e √±ande darnga sekndorde …ìe: …óe lepte kawru…óon …óe de woni ko pennatna …óon ka aduna nde nelaa…óo habri on."
  83,18,"Huunde nde wonah no,mbaadinir…óon nih wonde haasboore e njo…ìdi ngaratah, deftere …óoftii…ìe nani ka Illiyiina ko toon woni to martaba …ìur…óo toowde."
  83,19,"Hol ko anndin Ma-aan nelaa…óo-hol ko woni Illiyyiina?."
  83,20,"Pellet deftere mum en ko winndaande, nde uytetaake nde …ìeydetaake."
  83,21,"Ina seedoo nde deftere …ìadii…ìe kala kammu ummaade e malayka en."
  83,22,"Pellet …ìeen heewa golle lobbe e …óoftaare ina e neema duumii…óo √±ande darnga."
  83,23,"E dow leece cu…óaa…óe ko…ìe ndaaroo…ìe faade e joom mum en, e kala ko welnata pittaalimum en."
  83,24,"Si a yi*ii…ìe nji*a e geece mum en batte neema ngam lobbere e yoo…óde."
  83,25,"Na yarna…ìe liggatoo…ìe mum en dola mbo mba…óirkon mum omndaa."
  83,26,"Balangol misku na uura haa e haa…ótirde mum, e ndii njo…ìdi teddundu yo da…óandiroo…ìe da…óandir heen, tawa ko e gollude ko welata Alla, e accude ko tikkinta Mbo."
  83,27,"Njaram …óam na jille e seewnde Tasniim."
  83,28,"Ndeen ko seewnde …ìurnde toowde ka aljanna laa…ìde pos, denndaangal goon…óin…ìe na njara heen."
  83,29,"…ìeen faajirin…ìe sabu ko…ìe ngonnoo e keefeeru, ho…ìe njalatnoo goon…ói…ìe ngam jalkitde …ìe."
  83,30,"Si…ìe mbirtiima goon…ói…ìe …ìe ngona e …ìii√±andirde ngam jalkitde e saboote."
  83,31,"Si…ìe nduttiima ka koreeji mum en …ìe ndutto ko…ìe weltor…ìe ko…ìe ngoni ko e keefeeru e sabootde goon…óin…ìe …ìe."
  83,32,"Si…ìe ceediima juul…ìe, …ìe mbi*a: pellet …ìee ko majju…ìe gaa e laawol peewal, sabu accude …ìe diine baabiraa…ìe mum en."
  83,33,"Alla wakkilaani …ìe reende golle mum en haa …ìe kaala haala mum en ko."
  83,34,"√±ande darnga goon…óin…ìe Alla njala heefer…ìe hono no…ìe njaldatnoo…ìe ka aduna."
  83,35,"E leece cu…óaa…óe ho…ìe ndaara ko Alla heblani …ìe e neema duumii…óo."
  83,36,"Ko goongo yo…ìraama heeferbe golle mum en …óebe ngollatno ka aduna lepte koynooje."
